data.description: Come check out this great brick home just outside of downtown Mabank! This home sits on approximately 2 acres with a nice metal shop and storage building. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 car garage, 1906 sq. ft., formal living and dining areas, a large kitchen with breakfast area and built-in desk area, and master suite with separate tub and shower. This is a great property for the price and won’t last long!
